5.1 What is the difference between HTTP and HTTPS?
Ans--

Feature,                   HTTP,                                                      HTTPS
Full Name,                 Hypertext Transfer Protocol,                               Hypertext Transfer Protocol Secure
Encryption,                None (Plain Text),                                         SSL/TLS Encryption
Port,                        80,                                                          443
Data Integrity,            Vulnerable to tampering,                                   Prevents data modification
